metadata.name: Carpe GM I
metadata.description:
Carpe GM frens! 

This is a limited edition tribute to the culture and the beginning of a new phase of creativity, experiments, and drop mechanisms in my work. Holders of this piece will be the first to access my new exclusive collectors-only Telegram chat, and will also be receiving personal Carpe GM shout-outs from me on Twitter for the rest of the week!

Plans for subsequent drops, burns, and community-building to come. Join me.

“Carpe diem! Rejoice while you are alive; enjoy the day; live life to the fullest; make the most of what you have. It is later than you think.” - Horace

“GM” - web3
